      "totalCount": 2200,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4199&rangeEnd=4273",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4199&rangeEnd=4273"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_28_2136-2167",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2136-2167",
      "markText": "如果婚姻是为了创造幸福而不是出于幸福，那么这样的婚姻很难成功。",
      "totalCount": 1785,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2136&rangeEnd=2167",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2136&rangeEnd=2167"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_23_2383-2414",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "2383-2414",
      "markText": "重视夫妻间的友谊，接受彼此的影响，在遇到分歧时要保持态度平和。",
      "totalCount": 1650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=2383&rangeEnd=2414",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=2383&rangeEnd=2414"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_30_6832-6897",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "6832-6897",
      "markText": "理解必须先于建议。我再进一步给你一个警告：如果对方没有问，根本不要给出建议。只要陪着他，倾听就是你能做出的最大贡献。",
      "totalCount": 1518,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=6832&rangeEnd=6897",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=6832&rangeEnd=6897"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_28_4651-4670",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "4651-4670",
      "markText": "人们为息事宁人而说的谎反而会破坏信任。",
      "totalCount": 1278,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4651&rangeEnd=4670",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4651&rangeEnd=4670"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_23_4903-4940",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "4903-4940",
      "markText": "绝对的信任会为你节省大量的时间，也让你可以放心大胆地做事，而不是提心吊胆。",
      "totalCount": 1162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=4903&rangeEnd=4940",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=4903&rangeEnd=4940"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_24_4537-4611",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "4537-4611",
      "markText": "信任，不是一种在两个人之间生长的模糊不清的品质。当双方愿意为了对方的利益而改变自己的行为时，信任就产生了。亲密关系中的信任越多，对彼此的关爱就越多。",
      "totalCount": 1156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4537&rangeEnd=4611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4537&rangeEnd=4611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_32_1540-1579",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "1540-1579",
      "markText": "如果你不能陈述对方的观点并且令其满意，就不要妄想说服对方、解决问题或达成共识。",
      "totalCount": 1105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1540&rangeEnd=1579",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1540&rangeEnd=1579"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_31_2015-2098",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "2015-2098",
      "markText": "如果你曾对一个人寄予无比信任，将你内心最深的痛楚如实相告，而他（她）却非但不陪伴在你左右，还不予回应，你无疑会感到愤怒、惊慌和孤独。这种伤害会深深地刻在你的记忆之中。",
      "totalCount": 1044,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=2015&rangeEnd=2098",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=2015&rangeEnd=2098"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_28_2666-2759",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2666-2759",
      "markText": "亲密伴侣需要对彼此袒露他们的生活目标和意义。当伴侣无视或者拒绝讨论深层问题时，他们就只剩下浅层的承诺。想要避免这种情况，伴侣要特意花时间去讨论他们的目标和梦想，而不是坐等这样的时机出现。",
      "totalCount": 1003,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2666&rangeEnd=2759",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2666&rangeEnd=2759"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_25_1986-2049",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "1986-2049",
      "markText": "修复是婚恋关系的救生衣。修复的效果决定着婚恋关系的存亡。修复并不复杂。常用的修复技巧包括笑话、赞扬、握手和提问。",
      "totalCount": 880,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=1986&rangeEnd=2049",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=1986&rangeEnd=2049"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_25_5401-5452",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "5401-5452",
      "markText": "但中性情绪却是关系到婚恋关系最终结果的关键因素。那些大多数时间都处于无情绪状态的伴侣们最终会白头偕老。",
      "totalCount": 864,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=5401&rangeEnd=5452",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=5401&rangeEnd=5452"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_25_9271-9341",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "9271-9341",
      "markText": "滑动门时刻：当一个人表达出联结的需要时，另一个人的反应可以是拉开门走过去，也可以是关上门转身离开。这是发展亲密关系的关键时刻。",
      "totalCount": 864,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=713371&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=9271&rangeEnd=9341",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9a2321d05ae29b9a241382b?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=9271&rangeEnd=9341"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "713371_23_3435-3464",
